\f3\i\b \cf5 3. Overall Conclusion on iOS App Alignment
\f0\i0\b0 \cf2 \
\
  The iOS application is 
\f1\b well-designed, correctly implemented, and perfectly aligned with our MVP vision.
\f0\b0 \
\
   * The use of 
\f1\b MVVM, SwiftUI, and `RoomPlan`
\f0\b0  follows Apple's best practices, ensuring a stable and maintainable foundation.\
   * The current single-room scanning and estimation flow provides a solid base.\
   * The planned modifications (multi-room scanning via "scan-and-queue" and improved UX guidance) are 
\f1\b additive features
\f0\b0  that\
     fit seamlessly into the existing architecture. They do not require a fundamental re-architecture of the app.\
   * The app is ready to consume the more granular estimate data once the backend is updated.\
\
  We can proceed with confidence that the iOS app is prepared for the next phase of development.\
